OL,3,CGovernment urged not to weaken
OL,4,C'Hillsborough Law'
OL,6,FMPs have urged the Government not to
OL,7,Fweaken a law designed to prevent cover-
OL,8,Fups in the wake of major disasters, as
OL,9,Fthey call for the "Hillsborough Law"
OL,10,Fto be passed as soon as possible.
OL,12,FLabour MP Clive Efford warned Commons
OL,13,FLeader and Manchester Central MP Lucy
OL,14,FPowell that the Public Authorities
OL,15,FAccountability Bill, which will
OL,16,Finclude the "Hillsborough Law", should
OL,17,Fnot be changed under pressure from
OL,18,FWhitehall.
OL,20,FMr Efford asked for it to be passed
OL,21,Fbefore the end of July.
