OL,3,CGovernment urged not to weaken
OL,4,C'Hillsborough Law'
OL,6,FThe Government had said it needed more
OL,7,Ftime to finalise the Bill.
OL,9,FA draft Bill has been criticised by
OL,10,Fcampaigners, including the
OL,11,FHillsborough Law Now group, for not
OL,12,Fcontaining pledges previously made `
OL,13,Fincluding the duty of candour.
OL,15,FIn March it was reported that a
OL,16,Fmeeting between Prime Minister Sir
OL,17,FKeir Starmer and campaigners had been
OL,18,Fcancelled, with claims officials were
OL,19,Fattempting to have the contents of the
OL,20,FBill watered down.
