OL,3,CGovernment urged not to weaken
OL,4,C'Hillsborough Law'
OL,6,FMr Byrne told the Commons: "The Prime
OL,7,FMinister promised my city and all
OL,8,Fthose affected by state cover-ups that
OL,9,Fthe Hillsborough Law would be
OL,10,Fintroduced before April 15 of this
OL,11,Fyear ` the 36th anniversary of the
OL,12,FHillsborough disaster.
OL,14,F"Almost two months have passed since
OL,15,Fthe Prime Minister missed that
OL,16,Fdeadline.
