OL,3,CGovernment urged not to weaken
OL,4,C'Hillsborough Law'
OL,6,F"This is particularly disappointing,
OL,7,Fsince there is a draft Hillsborough
OL,8,FLaw ready to go, written by legal
OL,9,Fexperts, endorsed by survivors,
OL,10,Ffamilies, campaigners and proposed in
OL,11,FParliament by Andy Burnham."
OL,13,FThe Liverpool West Derby MP added that
OL,14,F"a failure to introduce a Hillsborough
OL,15,FLaw worthy of the name will be seen as
OL,16,Fa continuation of the betrayal of
OL,17,Ffamilies and survivors of Hillsborough
OL,18,Fand all those affected by state cover-
OL,19,Fups".
