OL,6,FLucy Powell said the Government was
OL,7,F"working at pace" and was co-operating
OL,8,Fwith families and their
OL,9,Frepresentatives.
OL,11,FShe said: "At these times, we always
OL,12,Fremember those affected by the
OL,13,FHillsborough disaster but particularly
OL,14,Fthe plight that they have faced ever
OL,15,Fsince to fight for justice and fight
OL,16,Ffor accountability."
